ZH: 我们今天一起去餐厅吃饭，我来结账。
EN: We went to a restaurant together today, and I will pay the bill.

ZH: 在超市购物的时候，请记得结账。
EN: Please remember to check out when shopping at the supermarket.

ZH: 饭店的账单已经算好了，你可以去结账了。
EN: The restaurant bill has been calculated, you can go and settle it now.

ZH: 请问在哪里可以结账？
EN: Excuse me, where can I check out?

ZH: 小费已经包含在账单中了，你不需要再另外付。
EN: The tip is already included in the bill, you don't need to pay separately.

ZH: 请问您现在就结账吗？
EN: Would you like to settle the bill now?

ZH: 这是您的账单，请您核对一下。
EN: Here is your bill, please check it.

ZH: 我们提供多种支付方式来结账。
EN: We provide various payment methods for checking out.

ZH: 如果您需要发票，请在结账时跟服务员说明。
EN: If you need an invoice, please inform the waiter when checking out.

ZH: 结账后，请将小票保存好以备参考。
EN: Please keep the receipt after checking out for reference.

ZH: 请您花几分钟时间结账，谢谢合作。
EN: Please take a few minutes to check out, thank you for your cooperation.

ZH: 请问，您需要顾客会员卡进行结账吗？
EN: Excuse me, do you need a customer membership card for checking out?

ZH: 这里是您的找零，请记得收好。
EN: Here is your change, please remember to keep it.

ZH: 我们提供货到付款和在线支付两种结账方式。
EN: We offer two payment methods, cash on delivery and online payment.

ZH: 请在结账前检查一下您购买的商品是否齐全。
EN: Please check if the items you purchased are complete before checking out.

ZH: 超过一定金额的订单，我们可以提供分期付款的结账方式。
EN: For orders exceeding a certain amount, we can provide installment payment as a check-out option.

ZH: 如果您需要开具增值税发票，请在结账时告知我们的工作人员。
EN: If you need a VAT invoice, please inform our staff when checking out.

ZH: 结账时，请保持队伍有序以节省时间。
EN: Please keep the queue orderly during checking out to save time.

ZH: 在线购物结束后，请及时结账以免订单失效。
EN: After finishing online shopping, please check out promptly to avoid the order becoming invalid.
